WEBVTT

01:40.000 --> 01:41.680
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

02:01.160 --> 02:02.520
YUXI CIGARETTE

02:07.880 --> 02:09.639
Stop looking.

02:10.520 --> 02:11.920
He is not coming.

02:12.000 --> 02:13.840
You should just come with me
to the cement factory.

02:13.920 --> 02:15.400
Let's wait a bit longer.

02:15.480 --> 02:17.120
He told the property management
on the phone

02:17.200 --> 02:18.040
that he would come in person.

02:19.880 --> 02:23.040
Trying to deal with someone like
Song Qingsong, you are still too green.

02:23.560 --> 02:25.680
Just this bag of stuff.

02:25.760 --> 02:27.440
It means nothing to him.

02:28.040 --> 02:31.000
-Why would he come?
-What if he feels guilty?

02:31.080 --> 02:33.240
What if there's something at home
he doesn't want anyone

02:33.320 --> 02:34.560
or the police to find?

02:35.200 --> 02:36.600
I think the one feeling guilty is you.

02:41.360 --> 02:44.160
Keep staring, and you will turn
into Meng Jiangnv.

02:47.400 --> 02:53.560
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

03:05.520 --> 03:06.360
What are you doing?

03:07.000 --> 03:09.440
That guy dared to harm Wolf.
I am going to cripple him.

03:09.520 --> 03:11.400
Do you even have a brain?

03:11.480 --> 03:13.000
Did you forget we have transformed?

03:13.080 --> 03:15.280
Still talking about knives and guns?
Put it away.

03:15.360 --> 03:17.960
Mr. Jin, you said it yourself,
we were going to deal with him.

03:18.040 --> 03:21.760
Do you know who owns that car
with plate 688?

03:21.840 --> 03:24.120
The boss of Qingsong Cement Factory,

03:24.200 --> 03:25.640
Song Qingsong.

03:26.400 --> 03:28.160
How many lives do you think
you have to mess with him?

03:28.760 --> 03:30.320
So we are not avenging Wolf?

03:30.840 --> 03:33.280
We need to figure out the situation first
before we take revenge.

03:33.880 --> 03:36.840
How did Song Qingsong
get involved with Manlang?

03:36.920 --> 03:38.120
Alright.

03:38.640 --> 03:40.080
That makes sense.

03:50.280 --> 03:51.520
Follow him.

03:55.400 --> 03:57.200
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

04:16.839 --> 04:19.519
If any words Song Qingsong said were true,

04:20.240 --> 04:23.880
every pig in Weiyang
would be climbing trees.

05:16.440 --> 05:17.680
Criminal Department.

05:17.760 --> 05:19.080
A Mercedes just arrived at the entrance.

05:19.160 --> 05:20.600
They say they are
the owner from Yuanlongli.

05:23.200 --> 05:24.720
Let them in.

05:25.480 --> 05:27.400
-Brigade meeting room.
-Got it.

05:34.280 --> 05:36.480
Come on. We'll be seeing pigs climb trees.

05:41.360 --> 05:43.040
Hey.

05:43.720 --> 05:45.120
Why the rush?

05:45.200 --> 05:47.560
Have you figured out
how to question him about Xu Meng?

05:47.640 --> 05:49.240
Go through every detail
and verify everything.

05:49.320 --> 05:52.000
As long as there are inconsistencies,
we will find a breakthrough.

05:53.080 --> 05:56.120
Song Qingsong
is the victim, not a suspect.

05:56.200 --> 05:58.840
What if he just takes his stuff
and leaves without saying anything?

05:58.920 --> 06:00.720
Tell me, what will you do then?

06:07.240 --> 06:08.320
So what is your plan?

06:17.440 --> 06:19.080
Very simple. Five words.

06:20.040 --> 06:21.480
We will work in tandem.

06:23.800 --> 06:24.840
How?

06:26.040 --> 06:27.000
I lead, you back me up.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.080
I ease him in, you pin him down.

06:29.160 --> 06:31.160
I play the good cop, you play the bad cop.

06:31.240 --> 06:32.080
Got it?

06:33.600 --> 06:35.680
Are you sure
that's really your real intention?

06:37.640 --> 06:39.280
Just tell me. Do you get it or not?

06:43.000 --> 06:44.160
SPECIAL TASK FORCE

06:44.240 --> 06:45.080
The good cop goes first.

06:53.760 --> 06:57.480
What is Song Qingsong
doing at the police station?

06:58.360 --> 07:00.640
Could the police have traced
the Wolf case back to him?

07:00.720 --> 07:02.280
Trace, my foot.

07:02.360 --> 07:03.800
If they had, he'd be here in a police car.

07:03.880 --> 07:04.880
Right.

07:07.240 --> 07:08.520
You just reminded me.

07:09.120 --> 07:12.080
If Song Qingsong
really had dealings with Manlang,

07:12.600 --> 07:14.960
-then we could…
-We can squeeze him for a big payout.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.200
Squeeze your head.

07:16.280 --> 07:18.880
Jeez. We need to think differently.

07:18.960 --> 07:22.600
Use this opportunity
to talk to Song Qingsong.

07:22.680 --> 07:24.720
Get him to throw us some business.

07:25.320 --> 07:29.200
That's called "Water flows downhill,
people move up."

07:29.280 --> 07:30.800
Move up?

07:30.880 --> 07:33.600
What Song Qingsong did before
was way worse than what we did.

07:33.680 --> 07:34.600
I…

07:35.320 --> 07:37.160
If someone like him can clean up his act,

07:37.240 --> 07:40.800
then I should learn from him.

07:51.840 --> 07:53.520
ID and letter of introduction are fine.

07:58.280 --> 07:59.680
This tea tastes terrible.

08:02.600 --> 08:03.760
Wait.

08:03.840 --> 08:05.880
The owner has to come in person
to claim the stolen items.

08:05.960 --> 08:07.160
Call Song Qingsong.

08:07.240 --> 08:08.640
Have him come himself.

08:09.160 --> 08:12.040
Officer,
I have already made it very clear.

08:12.120 --> 08:15.640
The house belongs to my brother-in-law,
but I have been living there recently.

08:15.720 --> 08:18.400
So everything in the safe belongs to me.

08:19.920 --> 08:22.480
Alright. Let's verify everything,
one by one.

08:23.200 --> 08:24.160
What do you mean?

08:24.240 --> 08:25.760
Where were you earlier?

08:26.320 --> 08:29.360
By procedure, we need to confirm
in person that the items are yours

08:29.960 --> 08:31.040
before you can take them.

08:35.039 --> 08:36.080
Please go ahead.

08:42.159 --> 08:44.120
What brand is the liquor?
How many bottles?

08:44.720 --> 08:47.040
Moutai. 53-degree Feitian.

08:47.120 --> 08:48.120
-Four bottles.
-Cigarettes?

08:48.200 --> 08:49.240
Zhonghua. Four cartons.

08:49.960 --> 08:51.080
Four cartons of Zhonghua.

08:54.080 --> 08:55.880
-Yuxi.
-Two cartons.

08:58.200 --> 08:59.560
Two cartons of Yuxi.

08:59.640 --> 09:00.960
Flip-top Yuxi.

09:05.240 --> 09:06.400
Belts?

09:06.480 --> 09:08.320
Two belts.

09:08.400 --> 09:10.040
One gold Rolex.

09:10.120 --> 09:11.680
Three gold rings.

09:11.760 --> 09:13.120
Five gold chains.

09:13.200 --> 09:14.480
Two lighters.

09:14.560 --> 09:15.800
Three bundles of cash.

09:15.880 --> 09:17.040
Bring everything out.

09:17.640 --> 09:19.240
How much cash?

09:22.320 --> 09:25.760
Hundred-yuan bills.
Three bundles. Ten thousand each.

09:26.560 --> 09:28.080
That makes 30,000.

09:33.600 --> 09:34.440
He.

09:34.960 --> 09:37.320
That number sounds familiar.

09:38.320 --> 09:39.440
Yeah, it does.

09:39.520 --> 09:41.240
I heard there's a rule on the street.

09:41.320 --> 09:45.320
Say it's a 40,000-yuan job,
you pay 10,000 upfront,

09:45.400 --> 09:48.480
then the remaining 30 after it's done.

09:48.560 --> 09:50.240
And there's usually a little bonus, right?

09:51.000 --> 09:52.640
At least

09:53.280 --> 09:55.320
two cartons of flip-top Yuxi.

10:03.720 --> 10:04.560
Keep going.

10:05.280 --> 10:06.560
I don't have all day.

10:06.640 --> 10:08.080
Have you checked everything?

10:08.160 --> 10:09.040
Can I go now?

10:12.720 --> 10:13.760
Darn it.

10:28.200 --> 10:30.080
My watch… Where is my gold Rolex?
Where is the money?

10:30.160 --> 10:32.000
-Where is my briefcase?
-What briefcase?

10:34.920 --> 10:36.440
Briefcase… There is no briefcase.

10:36.520 --> 10:37.680
You remembered it wrong.

10:37.760 --> 10:38.840
I am a bit confused.

10:39.560 --> 10:41.200
I have been here too long.

10:47.200 --> 10:49.400
You mean Song Qingsong's briefcase?

10:49.480 --> 10:50.840
No, no. I remembered it wrong.
There wasn't one.

10:50.920 --> 10:54.040
It had "Qingsong Cement"
written on it, right?

10:54.120 --> 10:55.160
I remembered it wrong.

10:55.240 --> 10:56.320
Something in that bag you don't want seen?

10:56.400 --> 11:00.040
Call Song Qingsong.
Tell him the briefcase is missing.

11:04.840 --> 11:06.440
Take the items.

11:06.520 --> 11:07.720
Get to Dahuihuang now.

11:10.040 --> 11:12.640
I still have work.
Is it done now? Can I leave?

11:12.720 --> 11:16.160
Are you sure that's everything?
Nothing else? A watch?

11:16.240 --> 11:17.720
-Cash?
-I am sure.

11:18.640 --> 11:20.000
That is all.

11:41.600 --> 11:42.760
"Build strength."

11:43.360 --> 11:44.680
What is that?

11:45.280 --> 11:46.960
"Forge the police…"

11:47.040 --> 11:48.320
What is that?

11:49.960 --> 11:53.880
"Build strength, forge the police soul."

11:57.800 --> 11:59.040
You don't recognize the "soul" character?

11:59.120 --> 12:00.720
What does it mean?

12:00.800 --> 12:03.560
Those two characters look a bit creepy.

12:05.680 --> 12:07.400
It has two meanings.

12:07.920 --> 12:11.800
One is ghost, the other is spirit.

12:11.880 --> 12:13.360
-Got it?
-Got it.

12:13.440 --> 12:15.040
I have plenty of spirit.

12:16.480 --> 12:17.680
Whose kid are you?

12:17.760 --> 12:20.160
My dad is He Yuanhang.

12:21.000 --> 12:23.280
That Officer He on secondment.
I have heard of him.

12:23.360 --> 12:25.280
Miss, I need to use the restroom.

12:25.360 --> 12:26.720
Do you know where it is?

12:26.800 --> 12:28.520
Yes. I will take you.

12:30.320 --> 12:31.240
Let's go.

12:35.400 --> 12:36.360
Xiaohe.

12:37.400 --> 12:39.600
Your shoelace is undone. Let me tie it.

12:45.920 --> 12:47.000
Miss, he is looking at your waist.

12:48.720 --> 12:50.560
-Don't go. You're a bad guy.
-Hey.

12:50.640 --> 12:52.240
Kid, you're mistaken.

12:52.320 --> 12:55.920
-Mistaken? Kids don't lie.
-Dad, there's a pervert here!

12:56.000 --> 12:57.960
-What have you done?
-What is going on?

13:01.160 --> 13:03.440
Let go. Is this your child?

13:03.520 --> 13:05.600
None of your business.
Sharp face. Dark circles.

13:05.680 --> 13:08.200
You look kind of creepy.

13:08.280 --> 13:09.400
Like a pervert.

13:10.960 --> 13:14.040
At such a young age,
your temper is already this bad.

13:14.120 --> 13:15.840
You'd better watch yourself
when you grow up.

13:16.440 --> 13:18.080
-Hey!
-I am just telling the truth.

13:18.160 --> 13:19.880
You do need to be careful out there.

13:26.280 --> 13:27.520
He,

13:28.040 --> 13:30.640
when we mentioned the briefcase,
his eyes went right.

13:30.720 --> 13:32.800
When we mentioned the cash,
they shifted left.

13:33.480 --> 13:35.920
He was lying about the briefcase,

13:36.000 --> 13:38.160
but the 30,000 in cash,
he was recalling it.

13:40.200 --> 13:42.320
The one who hired someone
is very likely him.

13:43.920 --> 13:46.520
He should be on his way now
to find Song Qingsong.

13:47.160 --> 13:48.600
Song Qingsong.

13:49.720 --> 13:50.840
Officer He,

13:51.360 --> 13:54.280
if you're going out, leave Xiaohe with me.

13:54.360 --> 13:55.840
I'm Liang Juan from the Analysis Unit.

13:55.920 --> 13:58.480
I'm on the night shift. I can take her
to the cafeteria later.

14:05.280 --> 14:06.920
Thank you, Officer Liang.

14:07.000 --> 14:08.280
-Not at all.
-Kiddo,

14:08.360 --> 14:09.840
I'll come back to pick you up later.

14:09.920 --> 14:11.880
-Listen to Ms. Liang, alright?
-Okay.

14:13.880 --> 14:17.040
So you are the new top graduate
in the Criminal Department.

14:17.880 --> 14:18.920
He is.

14:19.800 --> 14:20.840
Hello.

14:20.920 --> 14:22.880
You two work well together.

14:23.680 --> 14:24.680
Right, Xiaohe?

14:27.080 --> 14:28.160
Let's go.

14:29.520 --> 14:30.680
He's out.

14:33.880 --> 14:34.800
Wait.

14:36.560 --> 14:37.800
He Yuanhang.

14:39.120 --> 14:41.600
The cops are following him.
Should we still follow?

14:42.320 --> 14:43.360
Yes.

15:13.120 --> 15:18.480
He, just the Yuxi cigarettes
and Wu Shanlong's reactions aren't enough.

15:18.560 --> 15:20.720
Even if we follow him
and find Song Qingsong,

15:21.320 --> 15:22.520
we need a plan first.

15:22.600 --> 15:24.280
What plan?

15:24.360 --> 15:25.720
Get him back to the station first,
no matter what.

15:27.480 --> 15:31.120
What? Even a top graduate like you
consults me now?

15:34.320 --> 15:38.280
I have noticed your methods
can be quite effective at times.

15:39.000 --> 15:40.440
There are only three days left.

15:40.520 --> 15:41.880
If we don't use some tactics,
we won't get anywhere.

15:41.960 --> 15:43.960
This missing persons case looks simple,

15:44.480 --> 15:45.680
but the deeper we dig,
the more complicated it gets.

15:45.760 --> 15:47.280
It is like a maze.

15:48.320 --> 15:49.360
A maze?

15:50.640 --> 15:54.320
I do have a theory for that.
Trémaux's algorithm.

15:54.400 --> 15:56.600
Don't even start. My head is spinning.

16:12.680 --> 16:14.000
Is it funny?

16:21.000 --> 16:23.320
Come on. You sing. Go on. Just sing.

16:23.400 --> 16:24.480
‎Come on, sing it!

16:25.000 --> 16:26.120
Sing.

16:32.920 --> 16:35.480
-Director Li.
-Song Qingsong.

16:35.560 --> 16:36.960
What's your order?

16:37.800 --> 16:38.920
Where are you?

16:39.440 --> 16:41.480
-At the factory.
-At the factory?

16:42.320 --> 16:43.880
Do you know about the mine break-in?

16:43.960 --> 16:44.800
No.

16:48.520 --> 16:50.960
Well, I just got back
from a business trip.

16:54.440 --> 16:55.960
Are the documents still there?

16:56.040 --> 16:58.160
Still there? They have all been taken.

16:58.240 --> 16:59.840
The police are involved now.

16:59.920 --> 17:01.960
I've been told to issue a statement
declaring all the stolen documents

17:02.040 --> 17:03.120
null and void.

17:03.200 --> 17:04.319
Yours too.

17:05.040 --> 17:08.079
Director Li, the documents may be voided,

17:08.599 --> 17:10.720
but my money isn't, right?

17:10.800 --> 17:12.440
Are you out of your mind?

17:12.520 --> 17:13.760
Talking about this on the phone?

17:14.800 --> 17:16.880
Was the mine really robbed?

17:17.400 --> 17:18.760
-Or was it…
-Enough.

17:18.839 --> 17:22.000
Cut the crap. Burn the documents now.

17:22.079 --> 17:24.440
If anyone sees them, it's on you.

17:24.960 --> 17:26.119
Do you hear me?

17:27.040 --> 17:27.880
Hello?

17:27.960 --> 17:29.280
-Again.
-Song Qingsong.

17:29.960 --> 17:31.080
-Another one.
-Do you hear me?

17:31.160 --> 17:32.600
Trying to set me up.

17:39.920 --> 17:42.240
Mr. Liu, where are you now?

17:43.080 --> 17:44.720
Here's the situation.

17:45.240 --> 17:47.360
Something just came up on my end.

17:47.440 --> 17:50.320
My driver lost the documents.

17:50.400 --> 17:53.600
When you arrive, we'll talk…

17:54.520 --> 17:55.720
Liu?

17:56.440 --> 17:57.440
Hello?

17:58.560 --> 17:59.800
Hello?

18:08.920 --> 18:15.320
DAHUIHUANG NIGHTCLUB

18:39.320 --> 18:40.760
That fool Song Qingsong is not in the car.

18:41.600 --> 18:43.640
Then who is this idiot?

18:51.960 --> 18:53.880
Welcome, boss.
We are glad to have you here.

18:53.960 --> 18:56.080
Wasn't it plate 688?

18:56.160 --> 18:57.720
You sure?

18:57.800 --> 18:59.040
I'm sure.

19:03.600 --> 19:07.360
Mr. Jin, I know someone
who'll remember it better than me.

19:15.440 --> 19:16.440
He.

19:17.160 --> 19:19.440
-He.
-What?

19:21.080 --> 19:23.120
We are just walking in like this?

19:24.040 --> 19:26.000
If not, are we supposed to climb in?

19:27.920 --> 19:29.520
You've done raids here before, have you?

19:29.600 --> 19:32.520
Even if I have, it doesn't stop you
from investigating.

19:38.280 --> 19:39.160
What I mean is,

19:39.240 --> 19:41.800
should we

19:43.240 --> 19:44.800
coordinate a bit?

19:48.040 --> 19:49.760
You lead, I back you up.

19:49.840 --> 19:51.800
You play one role, I play the other.

19:51.880 --> 19:52.760
That one.

19:54.200 --> 19:56.280
This time, you're the one asking me.

19:58.320 --> 20:00.520
What do you mean by "asking"?

20:01.200 --> 20:02.280
We're partners.

20:02.360 --> 20:03.800
Exactly.

20:03.880 --> 20:06.960
On a case, you have to lower yourself
and act naturally.

20:07.040 --> 20:08.320
Let's go.

20:13.640 --> 20:16.320
Welcome, boss.
We are glad to have you here.

20:16.920 --> 20:18.920
Police. Get Ms. Xia over.

20:19.000 --> 20:20.160
Alright.

20:31.960 --> 20:33.640
Mr. Song, I brought it.

20:35.240 --> 20:36.360
Now?

20:36.440 --> 20:39.000
What's the point now?

20:39.080 --> 20:40.480
No, but…

20:40.560 --> 20:41.480
I brought it.

20:42.360 --> 20:45.920
Eight million, and I ended up
with a pile of scrap! Scrap!

20:46.760 --> 20:49.560
Li, you are dead.

20:51.360 --> 20:52.520
Officer He.

20:53.560 --> 20:55.480
Officer He, what brings you here today?

20:55.560 --> 20:56.440
Checking up on us?

20:56.520 --> 20:59.520
Don't worry.
We're running things legally now.

20:59.600 --> 21:00.760
We won't break the rules.

21:00.840 --> 21:03.920
You said that last time.
And the time before.

21:04.760 --> 21:06.120
We have been making improvements.

21:08.240 --> 21:10.200
Let me ask you,
which room is Song Qingsong in?

21:10.880 --> 21:13.240
What Song Qingsong?

21:13.320 --> 21:14.600
Never heard of him.

21:15.880 --> 21:17.120
What about Wu Shanlong?

21:17.200 --> 21:18.320
Which room is Wu Shanlong in?

21:19.040 --> 21:22.480
Officer He, I don't know who they are.

21:22.560 --> 21:24.320
I've never heard of their names.

21:26.120 --> 21:28.280
Ran, make a call.
Get the Public Order Unit over here.

21:30.400 --> 21:35.280
Okay. Maybe we should also call
the fire, commerce, and tax too.

21:35.360 --> 21:36.960
-We should call them all.
-Good idea. Call them all.

21:37.040 --> 21:39.480
-Alright.
-No need.

21:39.560 --> 21:42.640
There's no need to make a fuss over this.
Everyone is tired, right?

21:44.040 --> 21:45.280
Oh my goodness.

21:48.120 --> 21:49.440
What are you still doing here?

21:50.160 --> 21:51.520
Get lost!

21:54.200 --> 21:57.280
Mr. Song, getting angry
is bad for your health.

21:57.360 --> 21:58.720
Who the heck are you?

21:59.960 --> 22:01.880
Mr. Song, they're police.

22:05.560 --> 22:07.680
I'm He Yuanhang from the Nanshan Branch.

22:08.480 --> 22:11.040
I just got off work.
So I brought a colleague out to relax.

22:11.120 --> 22:14.080
We heard you were here,
so we came by to pay a visit.

22:14.160 --> 22:16.360
I cannot stand the cops. Get out.

22:16.440 --> 22:18.640
Song Qingsong, we have received a report

22:18.720 --> 22:21.040
that you solicited prostitution
at Dahuihuang.

22:23.720 --> 22:25.480
Who is making
false accusations against me?

22:26.120 --> 22:28.120
This briefcase contains
the payment, does it not?

22:33.040 --> 22:34.560
The things inside the briefcase
are important documents

22:34.640 --> 22:36.680
from the cement factory.
They're confidential.

22:36.760 --> 22:39.320
Without a warrant,
no one is allowed to touch it.

22:39.400 --> 22:41.040
I will call my superiors right now.

22:41.960 --> 22:43.040
It is a misunderstanding.

22:43.600 --> 22:44.640
It must be.

22:45.240 --> 22:47.120
How could Mr. Song
possibly do such a thing?

22:47.200 --> 22:50.280
Right, I almost forgot.

22:50.360 --> 22:52.240
I have something here
for you to take a look at.

22:52.320 --> 22:54.080
Do you know this woman?

22:54.680 --> 22:55.600
I do not.

22:55.680 --> 22:57.280
Let me remind you.

22:57.360 --> 22:59.120
Muse Foot Massage. Mengmeng.

22:59.840 --> 23:01.720
Just last week, you hit her.

23:01.800 --> 23:03.000
Nonsense.

23:03.520 --> 23:04.800
I never hit women.

23:05.480 --> 23:06.320
Do you have any evidence?

23:06.920 --> 23:07.880
If you have none, get lost.

23:10.960 --> 23:12.320
Mr. Wu,

23:13.520 --> 23:14.800
we didn't get a chance to thank you.

23:14.880 --> 23:17.920
If you hadn't led the way,
how would we have met Mr. Song?

23:19.400 --> 23:21.200
Mr. Song, they came on their own.

23:21.280 --> 23:23.680
You went to the station yourself
to claim the lost items, right?

23:23.760 --> 23:26.600
You said your brother-in-law,
Mr. Song, has treated you well,

23:26.680 --> 23:28.680
so why are you still raking in so much?

23:28.760 --> 23:33.240
Moutai, Zhonghua, a gold Rolex,
and gold chains.

23:33.320 --> 23:34.360
That's over a hundred thousand.

23:34.440 --> 23:36.560
Nonsense. You're slandering me!

23:36.640 --> 23:39.640
Mr. Wu,
you have been very cooperative today.

23:39.720 --> 23:42.280
You told the Criminal Department
a lot about Mr. Song,

23:42.960 --> 23:44.320
especially about that briefcase.

23:44.400 --> 23:46.560
We had no idea it meant so much to him.

23:46.640 --> 23:48.400
Even when Mengmeng merely touched it,

23:48.480 --> 23:50.520
he made sure she disappeared from Weiyang.

23:50.600 --> 23:51.920
You're framing me! Nonsense!

23:52.520 --> 23:53.800
Bastard!

23:53.880 --> 23:55.240
-You bastard!
-You let go!

23:55.320 --> 23:56.360
Qingsong!

23:56.440 --> 23:58.520
-If he goes too far, arrest him.
-They are…

23:58.600 --> 24:01.080
They are clearly trying to drive
a wedge between us.

24:05.000 --> 24:06.200
Assaulting police officers is a crime.

24:10.920 --> 24:12.720
The police are hitting me!

24:18.440 --> 24:20.640
-Qingsong, run!
-Stop right there.

24:20.720 --> 24:22.320
-Let go.
-Qingsong, run!

24:22.400 --> 24:23.520
-Stop.
-Qingsong.

24:23.600 --> 24:24.520
Vice squad!

24:26.240 --> 24:28.080
Vice squad!

24:28.160 --> 24:31.640
Vice squad!

24:32.360 --> 24:34.680
-Run!
-Vice raid! Run!

24:39.720 --> 24:40.760
‎Hurry! Run!

24:42.560 --> 24:43.600
Is that him? Right?

24:43.680 --> 24:45.360
-No. Not him.
-Is that him?

24:48.600 --> 24:49.720
This way.

24:51.560 --> 24:52.640
Leave now!

25:04.080 --> 25:05.080
Mr. Jin.

25:05.160 --> 25:06.600
The one who climbed down the pipe.

25:06.680 --> 25:08.640
That is him! That is him!

25:11.200 --> 25:13.640
You still recognize him
with that injury on his head?

25:13.720 --> 25:15.720
Mr. Jin, I never forget a face.

25:15.800 --> 25:17.840
-Bring him here. Hurry.
-Alright.

25:19.280 --> 25:20.680
DAHUIHUANG NIGHTCLUB

25:24.920 --> 25:26.400
-He, drive.
-Mr. Jin.

25:27.080 --> 25:28.080
Police.

25:31.040 --> 25:32.400
Fuck.

25:32.480 --> 25:33.960
One after another.

25:34.480 --> 25:35.560
What is this, Snake?

25:38.760 --> 25:40.080
Behind us.

25:55.800 --> 25:56.880
Son of a bitch!

26:14.280 --> 26:15.240
Faster. Go faster.

26:15.320 --> 26:17.160
This is just a Fukang.
He's driving a Benz.

26:17.240 --> 26:19.600
If Song Qingsong gets away this time,
it will be hard to find him again.

26:42.040 --> 26:44.920
Song Qingsong,
I will not let you get away.

26:45.000 --> 26:47.000
He, don't lose your head. Be careful.

26:47.080 --> 26:49.720
At this point, whoever eases off loses.

26:49.800 --> 26:52.280
He's cutting me off.
Then I'll cut him off too.

26:52.360 --> 26:55.160
If there's an accident,
we'll bring both him and the car in.

26:55.680 --> 26:56.600
That works.

26:58.880 --> 27:00.440
He, accelerate.

27:33.160 --> 27:35.760
Benz, here I come.

27:47.600 --> 27:48.880
Come on.

27:54.280 --> 27:55.440
It won't move?

27:56.080 --> 27:57.280
Hurry up.

27:57.360 --> 27:58.440
-I can't move it!
-They're gone.

28:11.480 --> 28:13.440
Song Qingsong, you scoundrel!

28:13.520 --> 28:15.720
You wrecked my car. I'm not done with you!

28:21.080 --> 28:24.520
Wu Shanlong,
didn't you say it was in the safe?

28:24.600 --> 28:27.040
What a coincidence
that the thief just happened to take it.

28:27.120 --> 28:29.520
Wu Shanlong, are you playing me?

28:29.600 --> 28:33.160
Stop yelling at me.

28:33.240 --> 28:35.040
Everyone has been yelling at me today.

28:36.040 --> 28:37.760
I'm telling you,
even if we got the documents,

28:37.840 --> 28:38.960
they're useless now.

28:39.040 --> 28:40.560
Useless?

28:40.640 --> 28:42.160
What do you mean? Explain.

28:42.680 --> 28:45.040
Dongshan Mine was robbed.
You know that, right?

28:45.120 --> 28:46.280
The bidding documents were inside.

28:46.360 --> 28:48.760
Song Qingsong is furious.

28:48.840 --> 28:50.800
He spent eight million
on a pile of worthless paper.

28:50.880 --> 28:54.320
You want to blackmail him
with that pile of worthless paper?

29:01.200 --> 29:02.200
The police came just now.

29:03.240 --> 29:07.000
They seem to be onto Mengmeng.

29:08.800 --> 29:10.760
If Song Qingsong gets arrested,

29:11.320 --> 29:12.680
neither of us is getting out of this.

29:14.320 --> 29:15.600
What do we do now?

29:17.000 --> 29:18.200
I know what to do.

29:21.840 --> 29:22.680
Hello?

29:24.120 --> 29:25.120
Hello?

29:55.640 --> 30:01.520
QINGSONG CEMENT

30:01.600 --> 30:08.600
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

30:13.080 --> 30:14.080
SPECIAL TASK FORCE MEMBER LIST

30:14.800 --> 30:16.760
-Xiaohe.
-Xiaohe.

30:16.840 --> 30:18.240
What major case is it this time?

30:18.320 --> 30:19.920
Four teenagers went missing
in Binchuan District.

30:20.000 --> 30:20.840
They still have not been found.

30:20.920 --> 30:22.680
Now the municipal bureau
is forming a special task force.

30:22.760 --> 30:23.920
Our district has to assist.

30:24.000 --> 30:25.080
Didn't they call you to join?

30:26.800 --> 30:28.320
Enough chatting. Meeting.

30:29.800 --> 30:30.960
We will go up first.

30:41.200 --> 30:42.960
Xiaohe, you're finally here.

30:43.040 --> 30:44.480
Captain Zhao has been looking for you.

30:44.560 --> 30:45.800
-For me?
-Go on.

30:47.680 --> 30:49.760
APPROVED

30:51.280 --> 30:54.120
-Captain Zhao.
-Come in.

30:54.200 --> 30:55.360
APPROVED BY ZHAO JIE

30:57.480 --> 30:58.600
Sit.

31:02.800 --> 31:03.920
Xiaohe,

31:04.680 --> 31:07.680
about Han Zi'ang's case,
I plan to assign it to you.

31:08.280 --> 31:09.320
Han Zi'ang's case?

31:10.520 --> 31:12.480
What about the one in Binchuan District?

31:14.920 --> 31:17.000
What, you think
this case isn't big enough?

31:18.480 --> 31:20.880
Of course not.
I wouldn't dare pick and choose.

31:20.960 --> 31:22.720
Captain, don't worry.

31:22.800 --> 31:24.560
I will make sure this case
is thoroughly investigated.

31:24.640 --> 31:27.680
About this case, Captain Qu
wrote a report yesterday.

31:28.200 --> 31:29.080
You can refer to it.

31:29.160 --> 31:30.080
Okay.

31:30.600 --> 31:32.760
From what we can tell,
it's most likely a prank.

31:32.840 --> 31:35.680
So, the focus is on cleanup
and calming the parents.

31:35.760 --> 31:36.920
Understood?

31:38.960 --> 31:41.080
CAPTAIN'S OFFICE

31:48.800 --> 31:50.040
One more thing.

31:50.800 --> 31:52.960
Sort out your family matters
as soon as possible.

32:04.800 --> 32:06.520
See? I told you.

32:07.040 --> 32:08.440
By seniority,

32:08.520 --> 32:11.240
Zhao Jie is still just a kid to me.

32:12.000 --> 32:14.920
He Yuanhang,
you should give up on that idea.

32:15.840 --> 32:16.880
I will not let you,

32:18.120 --> 32:20.240
or any of you, get involved in this case.

32:21.320 --> 32:24.120
Just treat me and Mr. Ran as helpers.

32:24.200 --> 32:26.360
No need to feed us. We won't steal credit.

32:26.440 --> 32:28.080
All upside.

32:28.160 --> 32:30.960
If you keep causing trouble,
I'll transfer back to the archives

32:31.040 --> 32:32.720
-and sit there doing nothing.
-No, no.

32:34.080 --> 32:35.960
I'm begging you. Please.

32:36.040 --> 32:38.600
Help Mr. Ran, okay?

32:38.680 --> 32:40.000
There is nothing I can do to help him.

32:40.080 --> 32:42.720
He Xiaohe, that is Mr. Ran.

32:42.800 --> 32:44.160
He watched you grow up.

32:44.240 --> 32:46.000
Have you forgotten how good he was to you?

32:46.080 --> 32:47.360
I have not.

32:48.200 --> 32:49.680
He's doing quite well now.

32:49.760 --> 32:51.760
Stop bothering him.
It's not good for either of you.

32:54.600 --> 32:56.520
He's just pretending he's fine.

32:57.160 --> 33:00.200
Since I came back, I have looked into it.

33:00.280 --> 33:03.200
I found that he's still avoiding
that case from back then.

33:03.800 --> 33:05.160
It's his demon.

33:05.800 --> 33:08.160
We need to help him face it.

33:08.240 --> 33:09.960
-Face it?
-Right.

33:10.040 --> 33:12.440
-And then?
-Then,

33:12.960 --> 33:16.400
he stays in Weiyang
and rejoins the Criminal Department.

33:16.480 --> 33:18.320
You're dreaming again.

33:18.400 --> 33:19.760
He's a university lecturer now.

33:19.840 --> 33:22.040
Can he just be transferred back
to the Criminal Department?

33:23.000 --> 33:24.840
Besides, he's doing great in Beijing.

33:24.920 --> 33:27.200
Why do you insist
on bringing him back to Weiyang?

33:27.280 --> 33:28.960
That's for later.

33:29.040 --> 33:30.960
Right now, let's talk
about the helpers thing.

33:31.040 --> 33:32.880
I'll be honest with you.

33:33.400 --> 33:36.400
Captain Zhao assigned this case
to me not because of you.

33:36.480 --> 33:39.200
Everyone thinks it's a prank.
Barely even a case.

33:39.280 --> 33:40.240
What?

33:41.600 --> 33:43.600
What kind of logic is that?

33:44.120 --> 33:46.480
Back when Xu Meng
and her father went missing,

33:46.560 --> 33:48.000
everyone said it was a prank too.

33:48.080 --> 33:49.240
Was it?

33:54.640 --> 33:55.600
Dad,

33:57.160 --> 33:58.600
stop dwelling on the past.

34:00.320 --> 34:01.440
Go home.

34:02.200 --> 34:03.680
I've got work.

34:06.040 --> 34:06.880
Hey!

34:17.520 --> 34:24.520
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

34:32.080 --> 34:32.920
Master!

34:36.120 --> 34:37.760
Master, thank you.

34:37.840 --> 34:39.600
Master, thank you.

34:39.679 --> 34:41.800
I really should have
listened to you yesterday

34:41.880 --> 34:42.920
and gone straight to Yuanlongli.

34:43.000 --> 34:45.639
Would've saved a lot of trouble.
Thank you so much.

34:45.719 --> 34:47.120
-Thank you.
-It's nothing.

34:47.199 --> 34:48.280
No big deal.

34:48.360 --> 34:49.400
How's your child?

34:49.480 --> 34:51.440
He is still unconscious.

34:51.520 --> 34:53.120
The police say he attacked
someone with a knife.

34:53.199 --> 34:54.280
How is that possible?

34:54.360 --> 34:57.160
The school wants to expel him.

34:57.240 --> 35:00.400
I really don't know what to do.

35:01.920 --> 35:04.040
But he did attack someone.

35:04.120 --> 35:06.600
Did anyone actually see it?

35:06.680 --> 35:08.440
Bring that person out
and let them face me.

35:08.520 --> 35:11.720
I want to see who it was
that knocked him unconscious.

35:12.440 --> 35:13.640
Master,

35:14.720 --> 35:15.840
you are experienced.

35:15.920 --> 35:17.240
Please do a reading for me.

35:17.320 --> 35:20.120
See whether my child
can get through this safely.

35:20.920 --> 35:22.200
I don't do fortune-telling.

35:22.280 --> 35:23.160
I only find people.

35:23.800 --> 35:25.640
Then please help me find the culprit.

35:28.440 --> 35:31.720
How about I find you an expert?
If he takes the case,

35:31.800 --> 35:33.600
your child's situation will definitely
be thoroughly investigated.

35:33.680 --> 35:34.720
I'll do whatever you say.

35:34.800 --> 35:36.640
Wait here, I'll call him out.

35:37.160 --> 35:38.560
Thank you, Master. Thank you.

35:41.400 --> 35:43.360
He really is remarkable.

36:01.960 --> 36:04.480
Hurry up. The mother is waiting.

36:05.920 --> 36:07.040
Move it.

36:08.320 --> 36:10.000
You're so careless.

36:15.520 --> 36:17.880
Ms. Wang, I have been looking
for you. Get in the car.

36:19.240 --> 36:20.760
Officer He, I'm waiting for someone.

36:20.840 --> 36:23.040
Han Zi'ang's case is now under my charge.

36:23.120 --> 36:24.600
If you want to find out the truth,
come with me.

36:25.760 --> 36:27.960
-But…
-Hurry, get in.

36:28.600 --> 36:30.320
-Alright.
-Kiddo.

36:34.880 --> 36:36.200
Kiddo.

36:51.720 --> 36:55.640
Ms. Wang, don't worry too much
about your son's case.

36:55.720 --> 36:58.520
The victim only has minor injuries.
It's considered a light offense.

36:59.120 --> 37:00.240
Trust us.

37:00.840 --> 37:02.240
We'll get to the truth.

37:03.680 --> 37:07.400
Ang is innocent.

37:08.400 --> 37:10.080
He's so young.

37:10.160 --> 37:14.160
If he grows up carrying that,
what will people think of him?

37:15.560 --> 37:17.960
He's in a private school now.

37:19.000 --> 37:20.400
Look at me.

37:21.000 --> 37:25.560
I pulled strings and spent
a lot of money to get him in.

37:26.960 --> 37:29.480
If he gets expelled,

37:30.920 --> 37:33.840
our lives will be ruined.

37:37.080 --> 37:40.480
I'll go to the school tomorrow
and speak to the principal.

37:41.800 --> 37:44.240
Thank you. Thank you, Officer.

37:44.320 --> 37:45.600
But I have one condition.

37:47.520 --> 37:48.640
Go ahead.

37:49.880 --> 37:51.160
Stop seeing that old man.

37:53.120 --> 37:54.600
Master?

37:54.680 --> 37:58.000
-Why?
-He's no master. He's my dad.

37:59.560 --> 38:00.960
He's a fraud.

38:01.960 --> 38:03.440
You've got some nerve.

38:04.800 --> 38:07.000
You tricked Song Qingsong?

38:07.600 --> 38:11.440
You think someone like him
is that easy to trick?

38:12.600 --> 38:13.720
He's suspicious.

38:15.040 --> 38:16.840
Just a few looks
and you call him a suspect?

38:16.920 --> 38:21.080
Where is the evidence? No evidence,
and now it's backfired on you.

38:23.400 --> 38:25.760
The traffic police called me.

38:25.840 --> 38:28.240
They said a Mercedes driver
reported you for rear-ending him.

38:28.840 --> 38:30.040
He wants 30,000.

38:30.720 --> 38:31.760
How much?

38:32.840 --> 38:33.720
Thirty thousand.

38:45.640 --> 38:47.040
-Done?
-Don't touch it.

38:47.120 --> 38:48.200
It's not dry yet.

38:52.320 --> 38:53.920
I'm not letting this go
with Song Qingsong.

38:54.000 --> 38:55.280
Keep an eye on Xiaohe.

38:55.360 --> 38:56.520
I'm going to stake out the cement factory.

38:56.600 --> 38:57.440
He.

38:58.760 --> 38:59.920
I was impulsive yesterday.

39:00.000 --> 39:01.240
-I'm afraid…
-Afraid of what?

39:01.320 --> 39:02.280
I'm not afraid of anyone.

39:03.680 --> 39:06.360
Dad, is that the bad guy who hit our car?

39:06.440 --> 39:08.320
I'm going too!

39:08.960 --> 39:09.960
Kiddo, be good.

39:10.040 --> 39:12.960
Stay with Uncle Ran today.
I'll pick you up later.

39:14.440 --> 39:16.600
Don't worry. I am not being impulsive.

39:16.680 --> 39:17.920
I have to keep an eye on Song Qingsong.

39:18.000 --> 39:19.720
-If not, he'll slip away.
-He.

39:20.440 --> 39:24.240
If we can't get him soon,
we'll have no other leads.

39:24.800 --> 39:26.920
I want to try that maze theory.

39:27.000 --> 39:29.360
We've only got two days left.
Try whatever theory you've got.

39:29.440 --> 39:30.480
-I'm heading out.
-Hey!

39:31.080 --> 39:32.520
Be careful.

39:39.840 --> 39:42.560
Officer Ran,
this is Luandongzi's statement.

39:42.640 --> 39:44.480
-We need you to verify it.
-Thank you.

39:55.440 --> 39:57.480
QUESTION: HOW DID YOU GET IN YUANLONGLI?
ANSWER: YOU'VE CAME TO THE RIGHT PERSON

39:58.520 --> 40:00.440
There's an underground garage
at Yuanlongli?

40:00.520 --> 40:01.760
Yes.

40:01.840 --> 40:03.600
Luandongzi said people who pass by there

40:03.680 --> 40:05.760
can avoid the cameras at
the security booth and building entrance.

40:08.480 --> 40:11.040
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

40:41.480 --> 40:42.640
Officer Ran,

40:42.720 --> 40:46.520
the entrance to this underground garage
was sealed a few years ago.

40:46.600 --> 40:49.920
There's only this small access door now.
You need a key.

40:50.840 --> 40:52.000
Where is the exit?

40:53.160 --> 40:55.560
Outside the compound. Also needs a key.

40:56.160 --> 40:58.080
Besides the property management,
who else has keys?

40:58.160 --> 40:59.320
Not sure.

40:59.400 --> 41:01.040
You'll have to ask Manager Qian.

41:05.400 --> 41:08.280
Officer Ran, I need to get back
to the CCTV room.

41:08.360 --> 41:10.880
I'll leave you here.
All the keys for New York Block are here.

41:10.960 --> 41:13.240
Return them to the property office
when you're done.

41:13.320 --> 41:14.640
-Thank you.
-You are welcome.

41:14.720 --> 41:15.560
I'm heading off.

41:15.640 --> 41:16.760
-Bye.
-Okay.

41:21.480 --> 41:22.400
Xiaohe.

41:24.680 --> 41:27.440
Uncle Ran,
this underground maze is so cool.

41:27.520 --> 41:29.200
Stay close.

41:29.280 --> 41:31.160
There might be rats running out.

41:31.240 --> 41:33.080
I'm not afraid of rats.

41:33.160 --> 41:36.240
I caught one this big at my grandma's.

41:57.560 --> 41:58.720
Xiaohe.

41:59.440 --> 42:00.320
Xiaohe.

42:01.480 --> 42:04.800
Uncle Ran. I caught a big rat!

42:04.880 --> 42:07.040
What are you doing? Let go!

42:07.680 --> 42:08.680
Who are you?

42:09.880 --> 42:11.920
-Stop shining that light!
-Manager Qian?

42:12.000 --> 42:12.880
What are you doing here?

42:13.520 --> 42:16.600
Someone reported
that the motion lights are broken.

42:16.680 --> 42:17.800
I came to fix them.

42:17.880 --> 42:18.880
SAFETY FIRST

42:21.560 --> 42:24.120
Does an electrician's work
need the property manager to handle?

42:25.160 --> 42:26.120
Oh, come on.

42:26.200 --> 42:28.080
Uncle Ran, don't believe him.

42:28.160 --> 42:30.440
He looks more like a thief.

42:31.080 --> 42:32.440
Watch your mouth.

42:32.520 --> 42:34.240
Whose daughter are you?

42:34.320 --> 42:35.640
Officer He's daughter.

42:37.000 --> 42:38.080
No wonder.

42:38.160 --> 42:40.280
Your dad and I are good friends.

42:40.360 --> 42:42.400
You should be calling me Mr. Qian.

42:42.480 --> 42:45.480
Save it. I'm not friends with a thief.

42:45.560 --> 42:46.600
You!

42:50.840 --> 42:51.920
Officer Ran,

42:53.240 --> 42:55.560
what are you doing down here?

43:01.200 --> 43:02.720
Stop coughing.

43:02.800 --> 43:05.280
That penny-pincher
turned off the motion lights.

43:05.360 --> 43:07.680
-Why?
-To save electricity.

43:07.760 --> 43:10.320
Tell me, what is he doing
with all that cement?

43:10.400 --> 43:13.400
-Building a grave at home?
-You two!

43:14.800 --> 43:15.760
Did you hear that?

43:15.840 --> 43:16.920
What was that sound?

43:17.000 --> 43:19.120
Could it be those two missing people?

43:19.640 --> 43:20.480
Are you serious?

43:22.640 --> 43:24.160
You two!

43:25.600 --> 43:27.280
-Oh my goodness!
-Who is it?

43:27.360 --> 43:29.880
Don't scare me. I'm afraid of the dark!

43:35.440 --> 43:38.280
You two, get out here now!

43:39.440 --> 43:40.560
Why aren't you at work?

43:40.640 --> 43:43.080
What are you doing down here? For what?

43:43.160 --> 43:44.600
Didn't you tell us to…

43:44.680 --> 43:45.680
I… Tell…

43:45.760 --> 43:47.240
Tell what?

43:47.320 --> 43:48.720
Get back to work!

43:53.080 --> 43:54.240
Wait.

43:57.560 --> 43:58.480
You dropped something.

44:09.520 --> 44:11.480
Officer Ran, I still have things
to do at the property office.

44:12.160 --> 44:13.680
I'll be heading up now too.

44:14.560 --> 44:15.600
Hold on.

44:19.360 --> 44:22.280
Besides the property management,
who else has the key to the garage?

44:25.320 --> 44:27.800
When Yuanlongli was first built,

44:28.320 --> 44:29.320
there weren't many cars.

44:29.400 --> 44:31.080
The vehicle entrance was sealed off.

44:31.160 --> 44:33.720
At that time,
only the property management had the key.

44:33.800 --> 44:36.880
But then, later on,
the Pattia Club opened.

44:36.960 --> 44:38.680
They were afraid of resident complaints,

44:38.760 --> 44:41.520
so they had their guests
and staff use the garage.

44:41.600 --> 44:43.600
The keys just couldn't be tracked anymore.

44:44.520 --> 44:45.400
Officer Ran,

44:45.920 --> 44:49.840
-I… I'll be going…
-Just go. Mr. Penny-pincher.

44:52.720 --> 44:54.360
You really take after your dad.

45:33.440 --> 45:36.880
SAFETY FIRST
